text: Elias Karvonen (born July 28, 1994) is a Finnish professional ice hockey forward currently playing for TPS in the Liiga.Elias Karvonen - TPS - LIIGA - Jatkoaika.com - Kaikki jääkiekosta (in Finnish) Karvonen began playing for TPS through junior setup in 2010 and made his debut for the senior team during the 2014-15 Liiga season.Profile at liiga.fi (in Finnish) He also had a brief loan spell with TUTO Hockey of Mestis during the 2016-17 season.LAHTINEN PALLOSEURAAN, KARVONEN JA BERGER LAINALLE TUTOON (in Finnish) ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish ice hockey forwards Category:Sportspeople from Turku Category:HC TPS players Category:TuTo players
